Name: DefaultGapped
Title: DefaultGapped
Params: -outfmt "10 qseqid qstart qend mismatch gapopen pident nident length qlen" -max_hsps 1 -max_target_seqs 1

Name: DefaultUngapped
Title: DefaultUngapped
Params: -outfmt "10 qseqid qstart qend mismatch gapopen pident nident length qlen" -max_hsps 1 -max_target_seqs 1 -ungapped

Name: tomkins2013
Title: Tomkins 2013 no max hsps 1
Params: -task blastn -outfmt "10 qseqid qstart qend mismatch gapopen pident nident length qlen" -evalue 10 -word_size 11 -max_target_seqs 1 -dust no -soft_masking false -ungapped

Name: tomkins2013WithMaxHsps
Title: Tomkins 2013 max hsps 1
Params: -task blastn -outfmt "10 qseqid qstart qend mismatch gapopen pident nident length qlen" -evalue 10 -word_size 11 -max_target_seqs 1 -dust no -soft_masking false -ungapped -max_hsps 1

Name: tomkins2018
Title: Tomkins 2018
Params: -task blastn -outfmt "10 qseqid qstart qend mismatch gapopen pident nident length qlen" -evalue 0.1 -word_size 11 -max_target_seqs 1 -max_hsps 1 -dust no -soft_masking false -perc_identity 50 -gapopen 3 -gapextend 3
